    rdfs:comment "Aggregation-slice classes (e.g. futuram:<drivetrain>_<component>_Y<year>): one summarized partition for ALL such classes. Each is a slice of a parent class along an aggregation axis via fq:sliceOf <parent> + fq:sliceAxis <strategy> (year and/or drivetrain), carrying fq:referenceYear or fq:periodStart..fq:periodEnd. Query any one like a normal class (fq:contains ...); pick the slice by its year/drivetrain." .

